								<wikidot:authorUserId>4058903</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I have a soft spot for articles 1) where a thing that should be made of one thing is made of another thing (see SCP-1970), 2) where there is a strong central image, and 3) that don't belabor the point. Dairy cow that gives milk steaks? That hits all three. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
