				<wikidot:authorName>DrBleep</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2887044</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like details of this, but like Magnus above said, it feels like something is missing. Its short, and to the punch for the most part, but the lack of expansion on certain aspects leaves me with more questions than answers, and not exactly in the good way in those respects. Mostly around the milking process.</p> <p>The addendum is weird and interesting enough that I'm not going to downvote because I think there is potential here for a little bit more implication.</p> <p>Novote for now.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
